data.description: THIS HOME CURRENTLY HAS A VA LOAN THATS ASSUMEABLE AT 5.25% INTEREST.JUST HAVE TO MEET LENDER REQUIREMENTS, DON'T NEED VA STATUS.Experience the ultimate Florida Keys lifestyle with this captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasting a bonus room, a sprawling fenced lot, and a luxurious swimming pool. Nestled in the heart of paradise, this gem offers all the allure of Florida Keys living while being just 45 minutes away from the mainland.This charming home is the epitome of coastal elegance, featuring three spacious bedrooms, providing plenty of space for you, your family, and guests. The two well-appointed bathrooms ensure convenience and comfort for all. But there's more - a bonus room awaits your creative touch, perfect for a home office, entertainment space, or a guest suite.Step into the backyard, and you'll be transported to a tropical oasis. A generously sized lot, securely enclosed by a sturdy fence, offers privacy and tranquility, making it an ideal playground for kids, pets, and outdoor enthusiasts. But the real highlight is the pristine swimming pool, where you can unwind, soak up the sun, and escape the Florida heat.What truly sets this property apart is its location. While you enjoy the serene and idyllic lifestyle of the Florida Keys, you're just a short 45-minute drive away from the mainland. This means you can experience the best of both worlds - island serenity and mainland convenience.Don't miss your opportunity to own a piece of paradise in the Florida Keys, where coastal living meets modern comfort. This property has it all - space, style, and proximity to the mainland. Dive into the Florida Keys lifestyle, relax by your pool, and create cherished memories in this beautiful home.Very reasonable insurances  current ratesHomeowners Insurance $735Windstorm $2,480Flood $2,378
